<p>I'm trying to modify my website URL for better SEO. Here's what i have so far:</p>  <pre><code> RewriteRule ^page-([0-9]+)/?$ /index.php?p=$1 [L,QSA,NC] </code></pre>  <p>i want <code>http://www.domain.com/page-10</code> instead of <code>http://www.domain.com/index.php?p=10</code></p>  <p>but how do i also match <code>http://www.domain.com/category/index.php?p=2</code> and rewrite it to <code>http://www.domain.com/category/page-2</code></p>